1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,060
= Episode 48 =

20
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:34,740
When

21
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:36,260
the Third Princess passed away,

22
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:38,900
Lady Zhang requested to be demoted

23
00:01:39,260 --> 00:01:42,460
and cut her pay to pray for the Fourth Princess.

24
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:45,500
Her love to children touches our hearts.

25
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:47,900
Unfortunately, she loses three daughters

26
00:01:48,260 --> 00:01:49,900
and is still ill in bed.

27
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:52,700
She serves Your Majesty for ten years

28
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:53,980
and gives birth to three princesses.

29
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:55,900
Still, she’s only a Lady.

30
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:57,380
And she never asks for a promotion.

31
00:01:57,980 --> 00:02:00,340
In danger, she risked her life
to save Your Majesty.

32
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:02,780
She didn’t protect His Majesty

33
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:06,100
out of a concubine’s love to His Majesty

34
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,740
but out of loyalty.

35
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:10,900
Seeing the Emperor in danger,

36
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:12,940
she, a defenseless woman though,

37
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:14,380
stood up to the ruffian to protect the Emperor.

38
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:16,300
She knew it was not in her power

39
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:17,700
but she also knew she had to stand up.

40
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:20,020
Her loyalty

41
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:22,260
is exemplary.

42
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:26,580
Madam Zhang does have it

43
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:29,140
to her credit.

44
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,700
You’ve made it clear, Xia Song.

45
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:33,860
I didn’t realize it.

46
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,420
I thought it was temper tantrum

47
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:38,540
and blamed her for her stubbornness.

48
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,780
I was up all night.

49
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:51,260
I’m exhausted.

50
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:54,620
Let’s call it a day.

51
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:56,380
The talk will be resumed

52
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,020
when Wang Sheng is arrested.

53
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:13,340
Is it true that father

54
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,660
is going to replace the Empress

55
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:15,740
with Madam Zhang?

56
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:18,140
Princess, please don’t speculate.

57
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:20,220
His Majesty treats Her Highness

58
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,180
with respect and trust.

59
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:23,220
It’s just…

60
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:26,740
It happened so suddenly last night

61
00:03:27,420 --> 00:03:28,580
that the unsolved case

62
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:29,460
has to be investigated.

63
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:33,180
And the evidence about the adultery

64
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:34,980
with Her Highness’s maid is solid.

65
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,620
Only a few officials believe it.

66
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:38,620
His Majesty doesn’t.

67
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,180
Father is the Emperor.

68
00:03:40,260 --> 00:03:41,700
He can do whatever he likes.

69
00:03:41,820 --> 00:03:42,740
All his subjects wish

70
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:43,820
to please him,

71
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:45,340
so they say what he wants to hear.

72
00:03:45,940 --> 00:03:47,260
They condemn Her Highness

73
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:48,340
and praise Madam Zhang

74
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:51,300
because father likes Madam Zhang

75
00:03:51,380 --> 00:03:52,380
more than Her Highness,

76
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,380
don’t they?

77
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:54,340
No.

78
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:55,620
Princess, it’s not true.

79
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:56,900
His Majesty…

80
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:58,380
Father urges me to learn knowledge,

81
00:03:58,380 --> 00:03:59,140
manners

82
00:03:59,220 --> 00:04:00,260
and classical literature.

83
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:02,300
But he gives all his love to Madam Zhang,

84
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,140
the most domineering

85
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,140
and ill-mannered woman

86
00:04:05,140 --> 00:04:06,140
in the palace.

87
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:30,580
Huaiji,

88
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:33,060
I told you before,

89
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:36,140
except father, Her Highness and mother,

90
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,900
you’re the closest partner to me.

91
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:41,420
I’m going to ask you a question.

92
00:04:42,220 --> 00:04:43,820
Do not lie to me for father’s sake.

93
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:49,260
I never lied to you, princess,

94
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:52,020
and I never will.

95
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:54,460
Good.

96
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:56,820
Then answer me.

97
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:59,020
Does father refuse to marry me

98
00:04:59,020 --> 00:04:59,900
to Cao Ping

99
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,260
because he’s decided

100
00:05:01,260 --> 00:05:02,540
to replace Her Highness

101
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,620
with Madam Zhang?

102
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:06,580
All I know

103
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,900
is that you’re His Majesty’s favorite.

104
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:10,980
So…

105
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:14,100
so the man he chooses

106
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:14,980
must be the best for you.

107
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,260
Yes.

108
00:05:19,220 --> 00:05:20,700
He doesn’t love Her Highness

109
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:22,340
and tries all means

110
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,860
to replace her with Madam Zhang.

111
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:26,300
Obviously, to him, the Caos aren’t the best.

112
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,700
Even if he makes Madam Zhang the Empress,

113
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:31,860
even if everyone else praises his wisdom,

114
00:05:32,260 --> 00:05:33,060
I won’t

115
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:34,340
recognize that woman as the Empress

116
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:36,180
and neither will I address her accordingly.

117
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,380
Let father lock me up

118
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:40,420
with Her Highness.

119
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,180
Fetch me

120
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,380
the jade comb and the rhino pin

121
00:05:56,540 --> 00:05:57,820
His Majesty gave me a few days ago.

122
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:00,580
Besides,

123
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,500
a few boxes of the blush I made,

124
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:05,500
several big pearls

125
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:06,980
from Cantonese businessmen.

126
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,380
Prepare two sets of gifts.

127
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:10,140
Send one

128
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:14,660
to Wang Gongchen’s wife

129
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:17,660
and the other to Wen Yanbo’s wife,

130
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:18,780
Mrs. Wen.

131
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,380
Tell them

132
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:24,700
I’m bored lately

133
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:27,660
and invite them over to talk

134
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:29,140
at their earliest convenience.

135
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:32,660
Yes,

136
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,260
I’ll prepare for it now.

137
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:37,020
But, madam, you’re not recovered.

138
00:06:38,300 --> 00:06:39,420
I’ve taken the medicines.

139
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:43,460
I’ll take all the medicines

140
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:47,180
and the tonics.

141
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:50,540
I’ll fight for it.

142
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:54,620
OK.

143
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:00,380
Lantiao,

144
00:07:03,460 --> 00:07:05,180
tell His Majesty tonight

145
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:06,780
that you’re pregnant

146
00:07:07,580 --> 00:07:08,780
and you want me

147
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:10,620
to raise your child

148
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,500
whether it’s a girl or a boy.

149
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:15,940
I’ll ask His Majesty

150
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:17,140
to promote you

151
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,420
and I’ll take no more

152
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,300
of your children.

153
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:23,020
Otherwise,

154
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:26,140
you’ll end up

155
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,340
like Yuan Cailing.

156
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:31,220
Although I’m not the Empress,

157
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,060
I’m pretty sure

158
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:35,820
I can do that.

159
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:39,660
Madam,

160
00:07:39,860 --> 00:07:42,260
I’m not sure of the pregnancy.

161
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,500
Don’t think that I’m inattentive.

162
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,380
As long as it’s about His Majesty,

163
00:07:48,220 --> 00:07:49,540
I miss no details,

164
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,500
nothing at all.

165
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:56,380
Your Majesty,

166
00:07:56,540 --> 00:07:57,460
Scholar Wen has arrived.

167
00:07:58,860 --> 00:07:59,580
Be seated.

168
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:14,460
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =

169
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:15,780
Forgive me, Your Majesty,

170
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:17,900
what is it that you summon me

171
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:18,900
for?

172
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:21,340
You’re the Military Governor of Hebei Province

173
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,940
and are going to leave tomorrow

174
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:26,340
for Qinghe County to subdue the rebellion.

175
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:27,820
Here

176
00:08:30,260 --> 00:08:31,420
are a few books for you.

177
00:08:44,660 --> 00:08:46,780
I don’t understand.

178
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:50,220
Can they help me with the rebellion?

179
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:52,140
I know

180
00:08:52,820 --> 00:08:55,180
you must have read all the battlefield reports

181
00:08:55,180 --> 00:08:56,260
from Qinghe County,

182
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:57,820
proposals from local officials

183
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:00,540
and books on the art of war and formations

184
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:03,260
to subdue the rebellion as soon as possible.

185
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:05,180
But,

186
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,460
do you know well

187
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:07,660
about the rebel leader

188
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:09,420
and who he is?

189
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:11,660
The rebel leader, Wang Ze,

190
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,740
is from Zhuozhou.

191
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:14,460
He moved to Qinghe and herded sheep due to famine.

192
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:15,820
Later he enlisted in the Xuanyi Army

193
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:16,860
and was promoted a low-ranking officer.

194
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:18,340
He believes in Maitreya Sect,

195
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:20,420
deceives soldiers with heresies,

196
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:23,140
and instigates rebellion with the forces

197
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:24,420
from Dezhou and Jinan.

198
00:09:35,060 --> 00:09:36,260
Maitreya Sect?

199
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:39,980
The Maitreya Sect

200
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:42,860
originates at the turn of the fifth century.

201
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:44,900
It advocates killing

202
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:46,420
and excels in drugs.

203
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:47,980
The drugs make people

204
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,580
forget their families

205
00:09:49,940 --> 00:09:51,220
and kill indiscriminately.

206
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:55,700
The sect was destroyed by Yuan Yao of North Wei.

207
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:01,140
Your Majesty, you believe

208
00:10:01,420 --> 00:10:03,580
knowledge about the cult

209
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:06,020
is helpful with the rebellion?

210
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,620
Your Majesty, do you have doubt

211
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:13,900
that last night’s incident is related to the cult?

212
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:15,940
I heard rumors

213
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:19,020
that the culprit lost his mind

214
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:19,940
and made unusual behaviors.

215
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:21,100
It’s more like that he took

216
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,420
a drug like Powder of Five Minerals.

217
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:25,500
Or maybe,

218
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:27,860
last night’s incident

219
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:30,500
is related to the rebellion in Qinghe County.

220
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:35,020
I want the rebellion to be subdued

221
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:36,900
and the culprit of last night’s incident
to be arrested.

222
00:10:37,300 --> 00:10:38,300
But I

223
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:39,500
give books to you

224
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,820
for the consideration

225
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:44,700
of not rebellion and the incident only.

226
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:46,940
I’m thinking...

227
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:48,620
This man is merely a farmer.

228
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:50,220
How does he fall

229
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:53,260
to the cult which instigates killing
in the name of Buddha,

230
00:10:53,700 --> 00:10:55,060
bewitch the others

231
00:10:55,900 --> 00:10:57,060
to kill without mercy

232
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:58,900
and instigate the rebellion?

233
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:02,740
I can’t understand, either.

234
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:05,740
Kill one and you’ll become Level One Bodhisattva.

235
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:09,300
Such cruel and absurd speeches

236
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:10,900
spread like a plague

237
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:13,540
among the people.

238
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,300
Take these.

239
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:26,060
Be careful.

240
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,180
These are forbidden publications

241
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:30,300
which are used by the cult to poison mind.

242
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,380
You won’t find any in the Capital.

243
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:35,420
These are my personal collections.

244
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:42,580
These filthy publications

245
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:44,580
can’t be spread out among the people

246
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:45,740
and bewitch more.

247
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,340
However,

248
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:50,660
you need to know the origins of the cult

249
00:11:50,980 --> 00:11:52,700
and how it bewitches the people.

250
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:55,060
We need to know what the cause is

251
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:56,460
to apply the right remedy to a disease

252
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:57,820
so that it can be cured for good.

253
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:00,460
You’re right, Your Majesty.

254
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:02,300
I’m too simple-minded.

255
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:05,260
All I can think of is to subdue the rebellion

256
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:07,740
and kill all rebels in Qinghe County.

257
00:12:10,780 --> 00:12:12,540
Kill all rebels.

258
00:12:16,260 --> 00:12:18,060
Aren’t rebels to be killed

259
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:19,660
once

260
00:12:20,940 --> 00:12:23,180
the people of Song?

261
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:27,140
I’m touched and admire

262
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:30,460
Your Majesty’s love to the people.

263
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:38,340
I’m ashamed of my shallow views.

264
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:41,820
For days, I’ve been thinking
how to defeat the rebels.

265
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:43,780
It never occurs to me

266
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:46,140
why the once good people

267
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:47,740
were converted to rebels

268
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,260
and how to prevent the good people

269
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:52,300
from being turned to rebels.

270
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:02,500
You’ll leave the palace in a few days, won’t you?

271
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:05,580
Be very careful lately.

272
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:06,860
= Ms. Xiu =
Don’t…

273
00:13:07,660 --> 00:13:08,860
Don’t contact with people outside the palace.

274
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:11,540
I was questioned

275
00:13:13,140 --> 00:13:14,300
by the Bureau of Clothing today

276
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:16,340
if it belongs to a maid from the Hall of Peace.

277
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:18,380
There are rumors out there

278
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:21,020
that the maid is a painter’s lover.

279
00:13:22,060 --> 00:13:23,020
And the painter

280
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:25,060
is the renowned artist, Cui Bai.

281
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:28,980
Anyway, be careful.

282
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:30,940
I don’t believe Ling’er

283
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:32,620
would engage in conspiracy.

284
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:34,660
It’ll be dangerous these days.

285
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:36,500
Be very careful.

286
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:49,820
Huaiji.

287
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:51,940
Your Majesty.

288
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:56,020
Are you still shocked by the incident?

289
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:00,580
What’s in your mind?

290
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:04,980
I’m curious

291
00:15:05,860 --> 00:15:08,140
what magic the cult’s publications

292
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:09,020
you gave to Scholar Wen

293
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:10,820
have

294
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:13,260
to make people lose their minds.

295
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:16,180
When you’re outside,

296
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:19,020
do you know anyone who cheats people

297
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:20,660
out of their money with superstitions?

298
00:15:22,020 --> 00:15:22,780
Yes.

299
00:15:24,380 --> 00:15:25,780
My aunt is tightfisted,

300
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:28,860
but she spends thousands of coppers on rituals

301
00:15:29,140 --> 00:15:30,460
each year

302
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:31,820
to protect our family business.

303
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:33,980
My mother

304
00:15:36,620 --> 00:15:37,780
didn’t believe most of superstitions.

305
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:40,340
But each time someone suggested her

306
00:15:40,340 --> 00:15:41,620
to pray to the Immortal of Letters

307
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:42,820
for my good scores in examination,

308
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,740
she was generous

309
00:15:45,060 --> 00:15:46,340
and did everything she had been told.

310
00:15:47,740 --> 00:15:49,420
She even made me drink tea made of burned incense.

311
00:15:50,940 --> 00:15:52,100
There was a Granny Li.

312
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:54,780
She was unable to walk.

313
00:15:55,820 --> 00:15:57,220
Physicians said it couldn’t be cured.

314
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:00,180
But she listened to a Taoist’s suggestion

315
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:02,140
that keeping a ghost can…

316
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:07,900
The reason why these words can bewitch people

317
00:16:08,660 --> 00:16:10,420
is that people hold

318
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,900
obsession, greed

319
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:13,860
and unrealistic dreams.

320
00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:17,380
It’s common in the people.

321
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,860
Is it not in scholars and officials,

322
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:24,060
noble ladies,

323
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,740
concubines,

324
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,220
Madam Zhang,

325
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:29,420
the Empress

326
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:32,420
or even me?

327
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:35,940
It’s not only

328
00:16:36,220 --> 00:16:37,740
the Maitreya Sect that bewitches people.

329
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:41,180
Everything that poisons minds and behaviors

330
00:16:41,900 --> 00:16:42,940
is the Maitreya Sect.

331
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:46,140
Is that why Your Majesty speak for Ling’er?

332
00:16:48,940 --> 00:16:50,860
She’s just one of the victims.

333
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:53,860
If everyone can be bewitched,

334
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:57,260
she isn’t totally evil.

335
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,540
She didn’t engage in conspiracy.

336
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:03,340
So Your Majesty, you regard her as a poor victim

337
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:04,860
who should be spared.

338
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:08,780
Huaiji,

339
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:12,540
you’re the only person

340
00:17:12,740 --> 00:17:14,020
who knows me.

341
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:20,300
But the Empress didn’t do anything wrong.

342
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:24,540
I don’t blame her.

343
00:17:28,740 --> 00:17:30,060
I never did.

344
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:33,820
I’m just angry

345
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:35,100
and don’t understand.

346
00:17:36,820 --> 00:17:38,900
She’s supposed to be my soul mate

347
00:17:40,180 --> 00:17:42,140
but why she goes different ways from me each time.

348
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:09,900
= Kill =

349
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:22,340
He has to die.

350
00:18:32,660 --> 00:18:33,500
Your Highness,

351
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:35,100
Wang Sheng died.

352
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,260
Yesterday,

353
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:40,340
Imperial Guards

354
00:18:40,340 --> 00:18:41,660
found him in the tower

355
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:42,700
northwest of the city.

356
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:44,820
But Yang Huaimin ignored

357
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:46,140
your order to keep him alive

358
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,180
and ordered the guards

359
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:48,700
to dismember Wang Sheng on the scene.

360
00:18:54,980 --> 00:18:57,620
Now all four culprits are dead.

361
00:18:57,740 --> 00:18:59,260
There’s no way to find the people behind them.

362
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:00,380
In the end,

363
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:01,100
only a few chiefs

364
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:02,420
of the Imperial Security Agency

365
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:03,780
on duty that night were convicted.

366
00:19:05,180 --> 00:19:06,460
That night,

367
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:08,660
it was Yang Huaimin who was on duty.

368
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:09,980
He should have been punished more severely.

369
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:12,340
But now,

370
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:14,260
Yang Jingzong and Deng Baoji

371
00:19:14,260 --> 00:19:15,620
are exiled from the Capital.

372
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:17,940
Yang Huaimin is only demoted

373
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:20,020
to a servant in the palace.

374
00:19:29,260 --> 00:19:30,100
Your Highness,

375
00:19:30,580 --> 00:19:32,820
it’s so unfair.

376
00:19:33,020 --> 00:19:33,860
Besides, I’m afraid…

377
00:19:33,860 --> 00:19:34,580
That they’ll…

378
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:36,820
Don’t you say His Majesty will defend me?

379
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:38,620
What’s to be afraid of?

380
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:41,940
Qiuhe,

381
00:19:45,540 --> 00:19:47,060
go back and pack up.

382
00:19:48,860 --> 00:19:49,820
Tomorrow morning,

383
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:51,940
you can go home.

384
00:20:02,660 --> 00:20:03,420
Your Majesty,

385
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:05,020
I’ve gone through

386
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,460
the proposals

387
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:07,940
submitted by all the officials.

388
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:10,380
What do they say?

389
00:20:11,420 --> 00:20:12,700
Right Counselor

390
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:14,460
and Assistant Administrator, Wen Yanbo,

391
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:16,660
Zhang Fangping of the Three Ministries,

392
00:20:17,140 --> 00:20:18,780
Deputy Executive of Privy Council, Wu Yu

393
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:21,100
think the disposition is proper.

394
00:20:21,820 --> 00:20:23,820
But they propose a thorough background

395
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:25,100
and behavior check on all Imperial Guards

396
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:28,140
and to cut off those who take drugs,
drink excessively

397
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:30,340
and conduct ill manners.

398
00:20:34,820 --> 00:20:36,780
Chief Executive of Privy Council, Xia Song proposes

399
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:38,900
to investigate

400
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:40,460
if the four are cult members

401
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:43,580
or collude with rebels in Qinghe County.

402
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:46,060
Same with Wang Zhi from Remonstrance Bureau,

403
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:47,980
he agrees with an investigation within the palace

404
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:49,540
to see if there are…

405
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:58,140
if there are maids having affairs with guards

406
00:20:59,020 --> 00:21:01,020
or even eunuchs.

407
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:03,020
If there are,

408
00:21:03,540 --> 00:21:04,500
they should be punished.

409
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:06,580
And their superiors should be questioned

410
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:07,740
if they help cover for them.

411
00:21:28,700 --> 00:21:30,500
Deputy Censor, Yu Zhouxun,

412
00:21:31,020 --> 00:21:33,060
Censor, Zhang Bian

413
00:21:33,540 --> 00:21:35,620
and Censor, He Tan

414
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:38,780
impeach Yang Huaimin.

415
00:21:39,780 --> 00:21:40,620
They believe

416
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:42,020
that night,

417
00:21:42,420 --> 00:21:43,940
Yang Huaimin was on duty.

418
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:45,620
But he’s derelict in duty.

419
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:48,500
The other managers of the Imperial Security Agency

420
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:49,980
have been exiled.

421
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:52,540
However, Yang Huaimin can stay in the Capital.

422
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:56,620
The punishment on him is too lenient.

423
00:21:57,220 --> 00:22:00,220
Everyone believes it’s unfair.

424
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:05,540
Imperial Guards lost mind due to drugs

425
00:22:05,620 --> 00:22:06,700
and excessive drinking.

426
00:22:06,820 --> 00:22:09,060
They set fire and startled the Emperor.

427
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,660
Those Imperial Guards should be punished.

428
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:12,980
Five men are exiled.

429
00:22:13,180 --> 00:22:14,260
They deserve it.

430
00:22:15,140 --> 00:22:16,020
= Madam Yu =
But why could Yang Huaimin

431
00:22:16,020 --> 00:22:17,980
who’s supposed to be punished severely

432
00:22:18,340 --> 00:22:19,780
secure a position in the Capital?

433
00:22:20,460 --> 00:22:21,500
It’s said

434
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:23,180
it was Xia Song

435
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:24,580
who proposed to His Majesty

436
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,860
that Yang should be questioned

437
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:26,980
in the palace.

438
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:29,980
He and Yang Huaimin are close.

439
00:22:30,620 --> 00:22:32,140
I guess he taught him

440
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:35,300
how to answer the questions

441
00:22:35,300 --> 00:22:36,380
to shirk responsibility.

442
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:40,820
They’re lenient on those close with Lady Zhang

443
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:41,780
and strict with the others.

444
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:44,100
According to my sister-in-law,

445
00:22:44,420 --> 00:22:45,900
though former Deputy Censor, Wang Gongchen

446
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:47,300
has been promoted to the Three Ministries,

447
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:48,900
the censor in charge of the questioning

448
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:49,980
is promoted by him.

449
00:22:50,300 --> 00:22:51,580
His wife and Madam Zhang

450
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:52,540
are good friends.

451
00:22:57,940 --> 00:23:00,100
He Tan accuses that Yang Huaimin indulged

452
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:00,940
his subordinates to kill the culprit

453
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:02,940
in order to destroy evidence

454
00:23:03,660 --> 00:23:04,540
and the witnesses.

455
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:05,860
He’s suspicious.

456
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,100
Huaiji,

457
00:23:11,860 --> 00:23:13,260
let me ask you.

458
00:23:22,900 --> 00:23:24,260
If we run an investigation,

459
00:23:25,340 --> 00:23:27,020
what are the possible results?

460
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,500
What consequences

461
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:30,860
will the results lead to?

462
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:36,140
Don’t pretend you don’t know.

463
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:37,860
I order you to be honest.

464
00:23:38,980 --> 00:23:40,180
You serve me so long.

465
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:42,220
If you don’t have your opinions,

466
00:23:42,260 --> 00:23:43,900
then I’m completely wrong about you.

467
00:23:44,460 --> 00:23:45,780
Even if it’s out of the imperial rules,

468
00:23:45,780 --> 00:23:46,620
a lie to your emperor

469
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:47,900
is a lie.

470
00:24:05,620 --> 00:24:07,340
Without solid proof

471
00:24:07,820 --> 00:24:09,900
that the four guards were under instigation,

472
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:11,180
now that

473
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:12,460
they’re all dead,

474
00:24:13,060 --> 00:24:13,900
we can only call

475
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:14,980
guards in charge of the security

476
00:24:14,980 --> 00:24:15,980
of Your Majesty’s chamber to account.

477
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:18,060
Given the current punishment,

478
00:24:18,540 --> 00:24:19,900
perhaps Yang Huaimin

479
00:24:20,540 --> 00:24:21,580
deserves more severe punishment.

480
00:24:23,820 --> 00:24:24,580
Go on.

481
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:27,460
If the four of them

482
00:24:27,540 --> 00:24:28,780
were Maitreya Sect members

483
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:31,940
and collaborated with rebels in Qinghe County,

484
00:24:32,540 --> 00:24:34,620
then it was a well-planned

485
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:36,140
conspiracy.

486
00:24:36,780 --> 00:24:37,940
It should be handed to Court of Judicial Review

487
00:24:38,340 --> 00:24:40,300
and the Censorate to question their chiefs,

488
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:41,460
officials who promoted them

489
00:24:41,460 --> 00:24:43,140
to be guards of the Hall of Politics

490
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:45,500
and all officials related

491
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:46,980
to the case.

492
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:49,460
It might be even related

493
00:24:49,460 --> 00:24:50,220
to ministers.

494
00:24:54,860 --> 00:24:56,380
If in the investigation,

495
00:24:56,820 --> 00:24:57,660
we find

496
00:24:57,660 --> 00:24:58,860
ambiguous evidence

497
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:00,260
proving Yuan Cailing is related

498
00:25:00,260 --> 00:25:01,500
to the guard’s conspiracy

499
00:25:02,060 --> 00:25:04,780
and she’s been executed by Her Highness,

500
00:25:05,260 --> 00:25:07,220
hence couldn’t authenticate the evidence,

501
00:25:07,580 --> 00:25:08,300
then…

502
00:25:14,260 --> 00:25:15,220
then Her Highness

503
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:18,260
is unable to prove her innocence

504
00:25:19,460 --> 00:25:20,500
and her integrity will be questioned.

505
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:23,140
Even Your Majesty trusts Her Highness,

506
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:25,460
it’s hard to stop others’ judgments.

507
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:33,060
Your Majesty,

508
00:25:33,580 --> 00:25:34,340
if I’m not too bold,

509
00:25:35,060 --> 00:25:36,980
maybe it’s a trap.

510
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:38,980
It’s not impossible.

511
00:25:41,580 --> 00:25:43,260
To frame the Empress?

512
00:25:45,100 --> 00:25:46,060
Why?

513
00:25:47,820 --> 00:25:49,060
Who will it be?

514
00:25:55,140 --> 00:25:55,860
You were

515
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:59,060
with Madam Zhang that day all the time.

516
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:00,060
Do you think

517
00:26:01,020 --> 00:26:02,700
she was faking it?

518
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,420
Madam Zhang’s anxiety was real.

519
00:26:06,780 --> 00:26:07,700
She almost went mad.

520
00:26:08,380 --> 00:26:09,620
I don’t believe she was faking it.

521
00:26:10,940 --> 00:26:11,740
Yes.

522
00:26:12,860 --> 00:26:14,300
She’s domineering,

523
00:26:14,380 --> 00:26:15,700
wayward

524
00:26:16,260 --> 00:26:17,500
and hostile.

525
00:26:18,940 --> 00:26:20,700
But she never fakes her feelings.

526
00:26:23,060 --> 00:26:23,940
So,

527
00:26:24,580 --> 00:26:26,060
the possible consequence of the investigation

528
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:28,100
is unrest in the court,

529
00:26:28,740 --> 00:26:29,780
ministers found guilty,

530
00:26:30,300 --> 00:26:31,300
the Empress’s integrity stained

531
00:26:32,140 --> 00:26:33,820
or Madam Zhang being hurt.

532
00:26:34,460 --> 00:26:36,060
They’re like vases that could be broken

533
00:26:36,060 --> 00:26:36,980
due to a few rats.

534
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,140
Or in other words,

535
00:26:39,620 --> 00:26:41,060
if we repel cockroaches on jade vases,

536
00:26:41,540 --> 00:26:42,740
we might not succeed,

537
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:45,100
but might break the jade vases

538
00:26:46,700 --> 00:26:49,580
that Your Majesty holds dear.

539
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,460
Huaiji,

540
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:57,580
make me

541
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:00,380
a cup of tea.

542
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:47,940
Ping.

543
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:54,460
Princess.

544
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:56,740
Ping,

545
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:58,140
what are you doing here?

546
00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:00,220
= Cao Yi’s Son Cao Ping =
My father and I took deer

547
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:02,180
and delicacies from mountains to Her Highness.

548
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:03,660
They have business to talk.

549
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:04,940
So I’m excused.

550
00:28:06,060 --> 00:28:08,860
As a young man, I dreamed to build a strong nation

551
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:09,980
and to be diligent in my duty.

552
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:13,340
I hoped I could uphold virtues,

553
00:28:13,820 --> 00:28:15,700
make friends with decent men

554
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:17,420
and spend all my life

555
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:20,500
making the politics clean and just

556
00:28:20,780 --> 00:28:23,620
and the nation peaceful.

557
00:28:25,540 --> 00:28:27,940
However, after all the years,

558
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:30,740
I realize one thing

559
00:28:32,420 --> 00:28:34,100
that daylight is paired with night,

560
00:28:35,220 --> 00:28:37,660
and flowers and fruits attract insects.

561
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:40,420
The good and evil

562
00:28:40,940 --> 00:28:43,700
are mixed up.

563
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:48,620
The emperor is supposed to tell them apart

564
00:28:49,460 --> 00:28:51,700
and safeguard good and remove evil.

565
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:54,900
But there isn’t

566
00:28:56,340 --> 00:28:58,420
a clear line setting them apart.

567
00:29:02,460 --> 00:29:03,460
The man on a stallion

568
00:29:03,460 --> 00:29:04,580
who brings peace to the people

569
00:29:05,380 --> 00:29:07,460
is only in stories.

570
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:10,940
Get up.

571
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,340
Don’t be nervous.

572
00:29:13,340 --> 00:29:16,100
It’s not a serious question.

573
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:25,180
I’m just

574
00:29:27,020 --> 00:29:28,380
having a hard time

575
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:31,580
and afraid to be seen through

576
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:34,580
yet couldn’t help

577
00:29:36,140 --> 00:29:37,540
wishing someone could understand.

578
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:46,820
In the past,

579
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:48,860
I instructed you

580
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:50,980
on purpose

581
00:29:51,140 --> 00:29:52,740
that when Zui Xinglai grows up,

582
00:29:53,340 --> 00:29:54,660
there could be a trustworthy,

583
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:56,100
smart and prudent man

584
00:29:57,260 --> 00:29:58,820
taking care of him

585
00:29:59,700 --> 00:30:02,620
and telling him what’s right and wrong.

586
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:05,500
See?

587
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:09,580
However considerate the plan is,

588
00:30:11,060 --> 00:30:12,740
it couldn’t change Heaven’s will.

589
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:21,500
♪ In drum beats, it’s dawn again ♪

590
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:30,580
♪ In time, we all grow old ♪

591
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:40,580
♪Let’s pray for good days ♪

592
00:30:41,380 --> 00:30:46,260
♪ To sing ♪

593
00:30:47,100 --> 00:30:54,220
♪ Proud Fisherman ♪

594
00:30:57,700 --> 00:31:05,460
♪ The river and sky are both vast ♪

595
00:31:07,340 --> 00:31:14,820
♪ No one can be young forever ♪

596
00:31:16,740 --> 00:31:24,500
♪ Don’t be afraid to be drunk and to laugh ♪

597
00:31:25,020 --> 00:31:29,460
♪ As you should know ♪

598
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:38,380
♪ Sorrow in life never falls short ♪

599
00:31:52,020 --> 00:31:52,820
Princess,

600
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,060
you should go back.

601
00:32:11,940 --> 00:32:12,700
Princess.

602
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:14,140
Huaiji,

603
00:32:14,460 --> 00:32:15,700
take me back.

604
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:32,500
I went to Pavilion of Phoenix earlier.

605
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,980
Xiao Ye’er told me you were out,

606
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,540
probably went to His Majesty.

607
00:32:38,460 --> 00:32:39,980
I just came back from His Majesty’s chamber.

608
00:32:40,500 --> 00:32:41,700
I know you weren’t there.

609
00:32:42,420 --> 00:32:43,180
So I think

610
00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:45,180
you may be bored

611
00:32:45,620 --> 00:32:46,700
and come out for a walk.

612
00:32:50,300 --> 00:32:51,420
Do you come

613
00:32:51,860 --> 00:32:53,300
to Pavilion of Phoenix on father’s order

614
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,140
to send snacks

615
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:56,500
or toys?

616
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:00,460
I come for you, princess.

617
00:33:04,100 --> 00:33:05,260
Not on father’s order?

618
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:08,340
You come for me?

619
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:15,380
I come to you

620
00:33:17,020 --> 00:33:18,500
mainly to tell you

621
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:20,740
that I think

622
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:23,060
His Majesty recognizes Her Highness’s importance.

623
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:25,780
His Majesty respects and trusts

624
00:33:25,900 --> 00:33:27,020
Her Highness all the time.

625
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:29,900
It’s just others might not see it.

626
00:33:31,100 --> 00:33:33,660
Please don’t let their misunderstanding

627
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:35,260
misguide your judgment.

628
00:33:36,980 --> 00:33:37,540
OK.

629
00:33:37,900 --> 00:33:38,980
I won’t trust others.

630
00:33:40,060 --> 00:33:41,220
I trust you.

631
00:33:56,180 --> 00:33:56,860
Qiuhe.

632
00:34:00,420 --> 00:34:01,860
Ms. Xiu, is everything all right?

633
00:34:02,220 --> 00:34:02,900
Mr. Zhang asks you to go

634
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:04,460
to him at the Imperial Office Bureau immediately.

635
00:34:05,060 --> 00:34:06,700
He said a censor named Wang Zhi

636
00:34:06,940 --> 00:34:07,740
reported

637
00:34:07,740 --> 00:34:09,220
that a culprit is related to Her Highness’s maid.

638
00:34:09,420 --> 00:34:11,220
That the conspiracy started in the Hall of Peace.

639
00:34:11,660 --> 00:34:13,380
He strongly proposed His Majesty to look into it.

640
00:34:13,380 --> 00:34:14,060
And he said

641
00:34:14,060 --> 00:34:15,100
rumors point to a maid

642
00:34:15,260 --> 00:34:16,340
of the Hall of Peace

643
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:17,660
who has affairs with an Imperial Artist

644
00:34:17,940 --> 00:34:18,820
and should be investigated.

645
00:34:19,300 --> 00:34:20,220
If necessary,

646
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:22,020
torture will be used.

647
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:28,620
This is a copy of His Majesty’s edict

648
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:30,060
to depose Empress Guo.

649
00:34:31,220 --> 00:34:31,940
Take it.

650
00:34:32,100 --> 00:34:33,260
Go to the Cabinet and wait outside.

651
00:34:33,820 --> 00:34:35,500
Censor He is debating

652
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,780
with Prime Minister Chen today

653
00:34:36,780 --> 00:34:37,980
on the Imperial Guards.

654
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:39,340
At dusk,

655
00:34:39,340 --> 00:34:40,620
they’ll come out.

656
00:34:40,740 --> 00:34:41,700
Run over

657
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:43,020
and pretend to carelessly

658
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:44,780
drop the edict on the ground and open

659
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:46,100
so they can see.

660
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,620
If they ask questions,

661
00:34:48,180 --> 00:34:48,900
tell them

662
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:50,100
Chief Xia

663
00:34:50,340 --> 00:34:51,540
asks you to get it for him.

664
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:54,660
Will Chen Zhizhong defend Her Highness?

665
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:57,340
The ministers

666
00:34:57,340 --> 00:34:59,020
don’t want to see an unrest palace

667
00:34:59,020 --> 00:35:00,860
or that the favorite concubine
who colludes with officials

668
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:02,020
and indulges her families.

669
00:35:03,780 --> 00:35:04,820
I’ll go to the Cabinet now.

670
00:35:46,380 --> 00:35:47,180
Depose the empress?

671
00:35:48,580 --> 00:35:50,700
Why do you hold the edict written ten years ago?

672
00:35:51,220 --> 00:35:53,780
His Majesty is meeting Chief Xia

673
00:35:53,780 --> 00:35:54,620
and Censor Wang

674
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:55,820
for the last two hours.

675
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:01,020
Let’s go to Hall of Politics

676
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:01,900
and meet His Majesty.

677
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:13,300
Cui Bai is only a painter

678
00:36:13,660 --> 00:36:14,500
who has nothing to do with politics.

679
00:36:15,020 --> 00:36:16,220
= Wang Zhi, courtesy name Zhizhi =
But as far as I know,

680
00:36:16,700 --> 00:36:18,740
he’s close with Ouyang Xiu, Cai Xiang,

681
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:22,580
Mei Yaochen and Su Shunqin.

682
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:25,780
It’s possible that they talked about politics

683
00:36:26,220 --> 00:36:27,100
in the name of poems and paintings.

684
00:36:32,300 --> 00:36:33,300
Is it an important matter?

685
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:34,740
Your Majesty,

686
00:36:34,780 --> 00:36:37,140
Chen Zhizhong, He Tan and Liang Shi

687
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:38,180
are waiting outside.

688
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:39,900
They said they have a crucial matter to report.

689
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:44,780
Since it’s crucial,

690
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,380
let’s discuss together.

691
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:06,300
I heard

692
00:37:06,340 --> 00:37:08,060
= He Tan, courtesy name Shengcong =

693
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:10,340
some people intend to defame

694
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:13,460
the Empress for a maid’s affair.

695
00:37:14,700 --> 00:37:15,500
I think

696
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:18,700
it aims to stir up the harem

697
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:20,420
and influence the court.

698
00:37:21,020 --> 00:37:22,340
They should be sentenced to death

699
00:37:23,340 --> 00:37:24,900
for their evil intention.

700
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:27,100
Censor He,

701
00:37:28,300 --> 00:37:29,860
should we look into the conspiracy?

702
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,740
Now a solid evidence

703
00:37:32,900 --> 00:37:34,060
is that one of the culprits

704
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:37,460
has an affair with Her Highness’s maid.

705
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:39,780
Although the maid

706
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:41,540
has been executed by Her Highness,

707
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:44,180
should we abort the investigation?

708
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:46,420
What if there are other maids

709
00:37:46,700 --> 00:37:49,860
in Her Highness’s chamber colluding with officials?

710
00:37:50,540 --> 00:37:52,620
We do need to look into the conspiracy.

711
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:54,660
But I think

712
00:37:54,780 --> 00:37:56,220
the first to be investigated

713
00:37:56,700 --> 00:37:57,700
is the man on duty

714
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:59,660
that night, Yang Huaimin.

715
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:01,660
He was in charge of palace security that night.

716
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:03,300
And he found nothing wrong.

717
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:05,100
Therefore, the culprit broke into the palace,

718
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:06,340
set fire and hurt people.

719
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:08,420
Then he disobeyed a

720
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:10,020
direct order which urges him to keep the man alive

721
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:12,460
and killed the only witness.

722
00:38:13,340 --> 00:38:14,500
Don’t you think

723
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:17,060
he’s the prime suspect of the conspiracy?

724
00:38:20,900 --> 00:38:22,180
I strongly advise Your Majesty

725
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:24,180
to hold Yang Huaimin accountable

726
00:38:24,620 --> 00:38:25,900
and investigate if Yang Huaimin

727
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:27,820
colludes with the culprit.

728
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,660
I propose that Your Majesty

729
00:38:32,020 --> 00:38:35,300
order an investigation on people

730
00:38:35,620 --> 00:38:37,860
close to the deceased maid, Yuan Cailing.

731
00:38:41,660 --> 00:38:44,340
It’s out of your loyalty that you worry

732
00:38:44,340 --> 00:38:45,740
about the palace security

733
00:38:45,740 --> 00:38:47,020
and propose a thorough investigation.

734
00:38:48,020 --> 00:38:48,900
But,

735
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:50,180
for these years,

736
00:38:50,500 --> 00:38:52,140
the harem has been harmonious

737
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:53,940
under the Empress’s lead.

738
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:57,540
All concubines behave accordingly.

739
00:38:58,140 --> 00:39:00,740
All eunuchs and maids perform their duties.

740
00:39:01,180 --> 00:39:03,740
I have no worries about them.

741
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:07,700
I didn’t sleep well lately.

742
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:10,020
I’m tired.

743
00:39:10,740 --> 00:39:12,740
Why don’t you go home

744
00:39:12,740 --> 00:39:13,580
and have some rest?

745
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,020
Your Majesty.

746
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:30,420
What?

747
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:31,620
The Empress asks for me?

748
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:36,860
Your Majesty made a promise to me years ago

749
00:39:37,180 --> 00:39:38,940
that I can ask a favor from Your Majesty

750
00:39:39,620 --> 00:39:41,500
as long as it’s not against the laws

751
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:42,580
or the palace rules,

752
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:43,580
Your Majesty will do me the favor.

753
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:46,260
Do you remember, Your Majesty?

754
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:49,300
I do.

755
00:39:50,980 --> 00:39:51,780
If I’m not too bold,

756
00:39:52,580 --> 00:39:54,140
I’d like to ask Your Majesty to honor your words.

757
00:40:01,740 --> 00:40:02,500
Mr. Zhang.

758
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:04,060
Yes?

759
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:07,380
the Prime Minister,
the Chief Executive and Censor He

760
00:40:07,420 --> 00:40:09,660
just left the Hall of Politics.

761
00:40:09,940 --> 00:40:11,420
It’s dark and the palace gates have been closed.

762
00:40:11,420 --> 00:40:12,220
They can’t get out

763
00:40:12,540 --> 00:40:14,380
so they’ll spend the night at Scholar Academy.

764
00:40:14,540 --> 00:40:15,460
They kindly ask you

765
00:40:15,820 --> 00:40:17,260
to sign on the Imperial Office Bureau for them.

766
00:40:19,660 --> 00:40:20,900
They went to the Scholar Academy.

767
00:40:21,340 --> 00:40:22,300
Will the gate be locked?

768
00:40:23,020 --> 00:40:23,660
No.

769
00:40:23,740 --> 00:40:25,380
They’re just staying for the night,

770
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:26,220
not drawing up edict.

771
00:40:57,220 --> 00:41:04,220
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

772
00:41:04,780 --> 00:41:11,660
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

773
00:41:12,140 --> 00:41:18,500
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

774
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:25,700
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

775
00:41:26,940 --> 00:41:33,740
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

776
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:41,100
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

777
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:48,700
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

778
00:41:48,700 --> 00:41:55,500
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

779
00:42:00,380 --> 00:42:03,900
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

780
00:42:04,100 --> 00:42:07,700
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

781
00:42:07,700 --> 00:42:10,900
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

782
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:15,300
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

783
00:42:15,300 --> 00:42:19,020
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

784
00:42:19,020 --> 00:42:22,580
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

785
00:42:22,580 --> 00:42:26,300
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

786
00:42:26,300 --> 00:42:32,060
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

